cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper deals with motion estimation of cardiac MRI videos using deep learning-based methods. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a novel online adaptive learning framework, which involves optimization and meta-learning, indicating a possible fit with cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of MRI videos suggests a possible fit with cs.MM (Multimedia), and the use of deep learning suggests a possible fit with cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
